Hey, did you know that on Mutt, ‘CTRL’+K will import public
openPGP keys attached to emails (with the right MIME type)?

That makes signing and sharing keys even easier ☺ 

Thanks [gollo](https://blogs.fsfe.org/gollo) for the tip!

